casebody.data:
Joe Nathan TUBBS
v.
STATE of Louisiana NO. 2018-KH-0229 Supreme Court of Louisiana. February 9, 2018

The application is transferred to the district court with instructions to the district judge to act on relator's motion for definitive ruling on claim requesting a nunc pro tunc determination of competency to proceed as relator shows by Inmate's Request for Legal/Indigent Mail receipt that the application was submitted on or about November 20, 2017. The district court is ordered to provide this Court with a copy of its judgment. A copy of the application is attached.
